definition: being changed over time so as to be e.g. stronger or more complete or more useful
details:
adjective
- being changed over time so as to be e.g. stronger or more complete or more useful
= example: being changed over time so as to be e.g. stronger or more complete or more useful

= example: (of real estate) made more useful and profitable as by building or laying out roads
- (used of societies) having high industrial development
= example: (used of societies) having high industrial development
